subject: Indianapolis 500 (Auto Race)
Celebrities
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick, who caused a stir two years ago by becoming the first woman to lead the Indianapolis 500, did not lead a lap Sunday and finished eighth in the race for the second consecutive year.
